VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT input\(\)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(eval\(|exec\(|subprocess|os\.system|os\.popen|sql|execute) && MISSING:(strip\(|isdigit\(|isnumeric\(|re\.match|re\.fullmatch)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potentially insecure usage of Python's input() function for user input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Use of Python input() Function.
